item.title: [525] Help with _js5connect
item.dc:creator: @adventurescape adventurescape
item.description:
@adventurescape wrote:

some 525 and 508 servers doesnt accept localhost (127.0.0.1 or 192.something.something lol)
if u want to login a 525, use kids scape 525 client and go in client and client2 and replace it with ur ip, and appletsub1.java i think also, mabye framesub1.java, after u replaced the ip with ur ip, compile the client and login!
~! I Hope This Helped !~

                         ~AdventureScape
